Class Diagram for Cleanly
Class: User

Attributes:

    UserID: Integer
    Name: String
    Email: String
    Password: String
    Rooms: List
    DigitalWorkspaces: List

Operations:

    Register(): void
    Login(): void
    ChooseSpace(): Space
    SetReminder(): void
    ShareProgress(): void

Class: Space

Attributes:

    SpaceID: Integer
    Size: Float
    Items: List
    DateLastCleaned: Date

Operations:

    GetGuidance(): String
    TrackProgress(): void

Class: PhysicalSpace (Inherits from Space)

Attributes:

    RoomType: String

Operations:

    AddItem(): void
    RemoveItem(): void

Class: DigitalSpace (Inherits from Space)

Attributes:

    PlatformType: String

Operations:

    IdentifyClutter(): List
    OrganizeFiles(): void
